    # pc "What?"
    pc "O quê?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:116
translate portuguese mills0_464983bb:

    # bs "When I see a young, sexy, masculine man working for me, doing whatever I tell him to do, I get certain thoughts."
    bs "Quando vejo um homem jovem, sensual e viril a trabalhar para mim, a fazer tudo o que eu lhe digo, tenho certos pensamentos."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:117
translate portuguese mills0_59186732:

    # pc "What kind of thoughts?"
    pc "Que tipo de pensamentos?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:118
translate portuguese mills0_ee9b49c6:

    # "She raises an eyebrow, and I can almost read her mind as she looks over my body."
    "Ela levanta uma sobrancelha, e quase consigo ler-lhe a mente enquanto ela percorre o meu corpo com o olhar."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:119
translate portuguese mills0_9453aa03:

    # "Then she seems to push all that out of her head and composes herself once again."
    "Depois, parece afastar tudo isso da cabeça e recompor-se mais uma vez."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:122
translate portuguese mills0_3ac1f82c:

    # bs "Oh we don't need to get into that."
