    # bs "Let's just say that when I see you working like that, it's hard to look away."
    bs "Digamos apenas que, quando te vejo a trabalhar assim, é difícil desviar o olhar."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:124
translate portuguese mills0_702cd0f9:

