    bs "Há muito trabalho para fazer. Volta ao teu e eu vou concentrar-me no meu."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:126
translate portuguese mills0_1ca80c77_3:

    # pc "Yes, ma'am."
    pc "Sim, senhora."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:129
translate portuguese mills0_0fdc08b5:

    # "I go back to cleaning and she moves back over to the conference table and sinks herself back into her work."
    "Volto à limpeza e ela volta para a mesa de reuniões e mergulha novamente no seu trabalho."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:130
translate portuguese mills0_f1272a0e:

    # "We don't talk much more for the rest of the day, and when it is time, I leave."
    "Não falamos muito mais durante o resto do dia e, quando chega a hora, eu vou-me embora."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:133
translate portuguese mills0_9a521cc3:

    # "The whole situation makes me feel uncomfortable."
    "Toda a situação me deixa desconfortável."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:134
translate portuguese mills0_0ed7a337:

    # "Mrs. Mills isn't bad looking for a woman her age, but still, it is weird."
    "A Sra. Mills não é feia para uma mulher da sua idade, mas mesmo assim, é estranho."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:135
translate portuguese mills0_3829b6ab:

    # "I wonder what I would do if she tried to do anything sexual towards me."
    "Pergunto-me o que faria se ela tentasse fazer alguma coisa de caráter sexual comigo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:136
translate portuguese mills0_1a3d193d:

    # "Would I argue with it and risk losing my job? Would I report her for sexual harassment?"
    "Iria recusar e arriscar perder o meu emprego? Iria denunciá-la por assédio sexual?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:137
translate portuguese mills0_943c6ec5:

    # "Or would I go along with it?"
    "Ou iria alinhar?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:138
translate portuguese mills0_22eaca64:

    # "Would I fuck Mrs. Mills?"
    "Iria foder com a Sra. Mills?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:139
translate portuguese mills0_421381fa:

    # "I don't really have an answer to that for now."
    "Por enquanto, não tenho realmente uma resposta para isso."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/mills0.rpy:140
translate portuguese mills0_99d09cb8:

    # "These thoughts race through my head as I drive away from the office."
    "Estes pensamentos passam-me pela cabeça enquanto me afasto do escritório."

